Name: Attack Of UNDO Zai
About the game: Human beings have uncontrolled destruction of the earth' resources, Aliens had sent Angle - Undo Zai to implement the fifth extinction of the earth. This is the final test for humanity. Defend Our World 4 player need to work together to protect our world from invasion of UNDO Zai. With 4 different ability characters and skills, player can play as a team to help each other challenge the game. Small Indie Game Single player shooting and challenge the normal or survival game mode. Multiplayer - 2 to 4 Player team PC shooting game, high definition furry anime characters in a non-stop action shooter. GAME FEATURES Fantasy 3D character art and animation in a non-stop action shooting and dodge attack. Single or team with 4 Player for the game challenge with 4 different title map. Normal battle mode and survival battle mode for challenge Steam Matchmaking and Lobbies Steam's peer to peer matchmaking API is built around to concept of a lobby can have up to 250 users in it and set of functions that enable users to find other users to play a game with.
